FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784510536
OL,3,CWho will get the big jobs in Burnham's
OL,4,Ccabinet?
OL,6,FIn this instance, several Labour MPs
OL,7,Fwho 100% will be in the cabinet have
OL,8,Ftold me - and I believe them - that
OL,9,Feven now, just hours before the
OL,10,Fcabinet will be announced, they have
OL,11,Fno clue what Burnham will offer them.
OL,13,FAnd to be clear, I am not talking
OL,14,Fabout obscure friends of the northern
OL,15,Fking. I am talking about household
OL,16,Fnames.
OL,18,FBut with all those caveats, my working
OL,19,Fassumption is the current home
OL,20,Fsecretary Shabana Mahmood will be the
OL,21,Fnew chancellor.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784510536
OL,3,CWho will get the big jobs in Burnham's
OL,4,Ccabinet?
OL,6,FIf such weren't the case, given all
OL,7,Fthe prior briefing, we'd know through
OL,8,Fnods and winks - because Burnham is
OL,9,Fpresumably savvy enough not to want to
OL,10,Fdestabilise the markets after all his
OL,11,Fcolleagues' conditioning for Mahmood
OL,12,Fin recent days.
OL,14,FIf it is Mahmood, it is a racing
OL,15,Fcertainty that the eminent economists
OL,16,FJim O'Neill and/or Andy Haldane will
OL,17,Fhave big advisory roles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
